<SYNC Start=251627><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=254604><P Class=KRCC>
<font color=#D2FFD2>총집편<BR>초록빛 나무 아래서
<SYNC Start=257965><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=259261><P Class=KRCC>
